description:
This is a 35 minute workout called '30 Minute Full Body Dumbbell Strength Workout [With Audio Cues]' from the channel Juice & Toya.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Tap in with us for a 30 minute full body workout that is built for all fitness levels. In this video we're taking you through a basic strength training session with audio cues to help you master each movement with correct form. All you need is a pair of dumbbells but we recommend challenging yourself with each movement by using multiple sets of weights if you have them. Be sure to drop a comment and let us know how your workout went with us!
